♪But the end of my journey
is still far away♪

56
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:58,742
♪Yet it never dies away♪

57
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:00,273
♪I will chase after my dream♪

58
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,836
♪The towering waves♪

59
