Once you arrive at Xiliu

86
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,079
and find the contact,

87
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,240
(Xu Xiaoyi, Recluse Tianyi)
on August 14th,

88
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,079
(Xu Xiaoyi, Recluse Tianyi)
he will bring you

89
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,720
to Kushuipu by the outskirt
